The Silver Age Green Lantern started out in Showcase 22 and ran for 3 issues before jumping to his own title that lasted 224 issues.

Included in this pack are the stories "Riddle of the Runaway Rocket", "The Invisible Destroyer", and "The Creature Who Wouldn't Die".
